		"HitBySlingshot": "Ow!$5#$b#What are you doing, @?! That hurts!$5",
		"WizardHouse_Entry": "Hello, Magnus, it's good to see you!/Ah, the energy is invigorating today.../Hm, I thought I saw it in here...",
		"SpouseFarmhouseClutter": "Erm...@, I didn't want to say anything before, but...$2#$b#It's getting very hard to navigate in here...do you need help cleaning up...?$2",
		"Spouse_MonstersInHouse": "@, help!!$3",
		"SpouseStardrop": "My beloved, you've been working tirelessly nonstop, and you've done so much for me...$4#$b#It isn't much, but...please, accept this token of my love.$4",
		"WipedMemory": "Ah...hello...have we met before?$2#$b#...No, I must be imagining it.$2#$b#My name is Aelin. It's a pleasure to meet you.",
		"AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved": "*gasp!*$1#$b#You remembered my birthday...! Thank you so much, @! I love it!$1",
