		"AcceptBirthdayGift_Hated": "...$2",
		"AcceptBouquet": "!!#$b#Y-you want to...with me?#$b#I-I...um...goodness, this is so sudden, but...#$b#I accept, @.$4",
		"AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Oh, this aroma...it feels so nostalgic...$1#$b#Mm...the taste is just how I remember...how wonderful. Thank you, @.$1",
		"AcceptGift_(O)376": "Ah, thank you, @! I was running quite low.$1#$b#Poppies have great medicinal properties. I can never have too many for my remedies.",
		"AcceptGift_category_flower": "Ah, I love flowers!$1#$b#Thank you kindly, @. I'll have to find a nice place to display these!",
		"AcceptGift_[O]417": "By Yoba...! Is this really for me?!#$b#Thank you so much!",
		"AcceptGift_[O]454": "This fruit...it has endured countless ages to bloom by your hand...#$b#Are you sure I can have this...?",
		"AcceptGift_(O)260": "A-ah, ahem...I, ah...don't handle spicy things well...thank you, though...",
		"AcceptGift_(O)420": "Um...are you trying to poison me, @...?$2",
		"RejectBouquet_AlreadyAccepted_Engaged": "@, silly, we're due to be married soon!$1#$b#Are you nervous, too? Don't worry, I'm not going anywhere.$4",
