		"RejectBouquet_NpcAlreadyMarried": "Um...I'm quite flattered, but...I'm happy in my marriage to {0}.$2",
		"RejectBouquet_LowHearts": "Erm...I'm sorry, @, but I don't really see you like that.$2",
		"RejectBouquet_VeryLowHearts": "...I'm sorry, I...can't accept this. I don't see you like that.$2",
