		"WinterStar_ReceiveGift_category_fish": "What the--?!$5#$b#This is--this is awful!$5",
		"WinterStar_ReceiveGift": "Thank you, @.",
		"WizardHouse": "I don't come here very often because the trip back and forth is quite tiring...$2",
