		"summer_1": "It's getting rather hot out...I don't handle heat well.$2#$q 328191/328192 summerheat_followup#How do you handle the heat, @?#$r 328191 0 summerheat_swim#I go swimming!#$r 328192 5 summerheat_cold#I eat lots of cold foods!",
